data.eml:eml: New insights in the taxonomy of Trichobranchidae (Polychaeta) with description of a new Terebellides species from Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Schüller, Myriam, Hutchings, Pat A. (2010): New insights in the taxonomy of Trichobranchidae (Polychaeta) with description of a new Terebellides species from Australia. Zootaxa 2395: 1-16, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.193948
